{"tid":1665714,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉:【好朋友Mohan Chugani誤中水炮車藍色噴劑 在此致以慰問】","createTime":"2019-10-20T16:11:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T17:35:22.000Z","uid":224270,"like":9,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cb8256d59a75592999992bf47defe8fd443c8cab","tid":1665714,"uid":224270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:11:51.000Z","msg":"【好朋友Mohan Chugani誤中水炮車藍色噴劑 在此致以慰問】<br />\n<br />\n傍晚驚悉我的好朋友Mohan Chugani(著名資深傳媒人Michael Chugani(褚簡寧)兄長)，下午於尖沙咀清真寺外被警方水炮車發射的藍色噴劑射中，身上染滿顏色水，需要即時送院治療。<br />\n<br />\n得知消息後，我已馬上聯絡他並致以慰問，他表示身上中了顏色水的地方感到赤痛，但經治療後已沒大礙，並已出院回家。 <br />\n<br />\nMohan Chugani 認為警方應就此事解釋及致歉，我向他表示特區政府素來非常重視與少數族裔人士的關係，我認為這是無心之失，但政務司司長張建宗亦應代表警方就此事致歉，明天我會親自將此訊息轉達予政務司司長，希望他盡快處理事件。"},{"pid":"a65251a04c8eb6341293efab73238812d1dfce61","tid":1665714,"uid":224270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:12:56.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"6f4e73a62760b0799a1b8cbe823c786d5c1739c9","tid":1665714,"uid":224270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:13:08.000Z","msg":"2/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8a32f0b3d99b4870c8405cfc1d326613da9b4e","tid":1665714,"uid":224270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:13:18.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"eeebe10bf8d5bbd64695598d3fbc4a5db53f3c97","tid":1665714,"uid":224270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:13:28.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"2d4ba9381c4de44dc4b809a1fe5d216771b51526","tid":1665714,"uid":202137,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:14:50.000Z","msg":"要人認底威嗰陣就識搬阿宗仔出黎"},{"pid":"3304f92d3b88453d430a8e0de6bdb027bbcd8094","tid":1665714,"uid":301989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:14:53.000Z","msg":"孽瘤姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23265c3ad6d2a98990f93a1a6b685af6143e24c1","tid":1665714,"uid":22310,"like":0,